{"tid":913243,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《鐵馬尋橋》兄弟團祝嘉穎當爸 唐詩詠：一定錫到BB燶","createTime":"2018-11-23T08:58:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T09:04:58.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e88b26a07a38c08561dff614571ec1950e4c5da0","tid":913243,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:58:04.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】對於鄭嘉穎及陳凱琳宣佈有喜，《鐵馬尋橋》兄弟團均送上祝福，唐詩詠說：「恭喜嘉穎，今年他最想有的兩樣事物（指老婆及BB）都有了，這個BB一定是萬千寵愛在一身，我們一班兄弟姊妹一定錫到BB燶！」馬國明則說：「恭喜恭喜！祝BB身體健康，一家人平平安安、幸福快樂。」更附上3個錫錫表情，想必也如詩詠所說「錫到燶」！<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WbQxqm.qShBL29DdyPNVhA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20181123f144706.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWbQxqm.qShBL29DdyPNVhA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20181123f144706.jpg&h=5eeed2d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29c4bbf2e84831a55a5db2a274e31ca79948b762","tid":913243,"uid":122535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"人在遠方 蟬沒有和唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38097c1a04f9339937c2877e6f30f451bf979e1","tid":913243,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:04:58.000Z","msg":"唐婆婆 幾時搵到人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}